          <avActivityHighlights>The fresh snow and the wind slabs are bonding poorly with the old snowpack.</avActivityHighlights>
          <avActivityComment>The fresh snow and the wind slabs that are forming in all aspects are bonding poorly with the old snowpack. &lt;br/&gt; Precarious weak layers exist in the old snowpack especially on northwest, north and northeast facing slopes. Avalanches can penetrate deep layers and reach quite a large size. Even single winter sport participants can release avalanches, including large ones.</avActivityComment>
          <snowpackStructureComment>The fresh snow and the wind slabs that are forming in all aspects are bonding poorly with the old snowpack. &lt;br/&gt; Precarious weak layers exist in the old snowpack especially on steep northwest, north and northeast facing slopes.</snowpackStructureComment>
